Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.54,0:00:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揭开了阿良良木月火的真正身份
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.48,0:00:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的故事也将画上终止符了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.96,0:00:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥你总是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.94,0:00:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是把我和火怜酱当小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.53,0:00:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是那个有点小聪明有有点烦人的年纪小的妹妹的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.49,0:00:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和我所爱的伙伴们的故事终于完结了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.23,0:00:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.14,0:00:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白金火大
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.31,0:00:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿良良木月火
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.63,0:00:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火炎姐妹中的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.27,0:00:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二个妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.50,0:00:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年纪小的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.23,0:00:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中学二年级
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.19,0:00:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四月出生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.20,0:00:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,14岁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.15,0:00:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B型血
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.97,0:00:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点狂躁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.01,0:00:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轮不到你说我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.47,0:00:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点小聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.62,0:00:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以对火怜酱发火
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.64,0:00:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不要对我发火
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.49,0:00:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,性格有双面性
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.84,0:00:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.48,0:00:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的女生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.17,0:00:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是不死身的伪物的故事
